org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.util

Class EntryIteratorWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.util.EntryIteratorWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type for the entry
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NativeEntryIteratorWrapper

    public abstract class EntryIteratorWrapper<T>
extends Object
implements Iterator<T>
    This is used internally to translate DataStore rows into native objects (using the appropriate data adapter). It also performs any client-side filtering. It will peek at the next entry in the wrapped iterator to always maintain a reference to the next value.
